```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph SC[Separate Catch Blocks]
        SC1[try block] --> SC2[catch IOException]
        SC1 --> SC3[catch SQLException]
        SC1 --> SC4[catch ClassNotFoundException]
    end

